From 2b75edafb4f720c22b9fdca3dfe5fbf1f0c5515b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hongxu Jia <hongxu.jia@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:09:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] third_party/com_google_highway: fix compile failure on clang
 22

Backport 5 patches from upstream https://github.com/google/highway
to fix the issue

 4201022d Detect clang 19/20/21, also allow user override
 6c595a1b Increase the clang version number to check for to disable `SVE/SVE2` tests.
 16bbb825 Update target attributes for changed clang AVX10.2 policy. Fixes #2697
 ad48f2bf workaround for inadvertent SVE codegen on GCC<14. Fixes #2689, thanks @kleisauke
 bd28820d mark avx10.2 broken prior to gcc 15.2, clang 20. Fixes #2671

Upstream-Status: Backport [https://github.com/google/highway]

Signed-off-by: Hongxu Jia <hongxu.jia@windriver.com>
---
